{"tid":1734399,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【克警賽果合理】愛國徽變「最喜愛香港藝人演警察」 單手Laughing都入圍","createTime":"2019-11-18T10:23:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T02:03:12.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c899bb513706b4c4c76c6c82f4a4893a30823c4c","tid":1734399,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:23:05.000Z","msg":"警察由胡椒噴霧到催淚彈放題，由警棍升級到布袋彈、海綿彈，甚至使用真槍實彈，仍辯稱屬「最低武力」對付示威者。示威活動持續超過5個半月，有人投訴被補後受到警察毆打，頭破血流不獲送院，甚至有少女報案，指在荃灣警署內被多名警員輪姦成孕要墮胎。<br />\n惡行歷歷在目，有警察奔向大灣區，光頭警長成為微博紅人甚至在大陸買樓，有人開微博新賬戶媾女搵人補褲。大陸人對香港警察趨之若鶩，微博賬戶「我有刑偵病」發起投票，題為「不作準的最喜愛香港藝人演警察」，上星期接受網民提名，超過50名香港藝人上榜角逐，包括劉德華、黎明、劉青雲、楊千嬅、甄子丹、黃宗澤、謝天華等。<br />\n昨日袁偉豪亦有就自己分組投票，同組對手包括「王浩信-盲俠」、「梁烈唯-唯唯」、「羅仲謙-謙謙」，投票結果相當符合國情，當中表現最愛國、在運動初期被惡搞上街的唯唯梁競徽（梁烈唯）以1,217票在小組中勝出，演《鐵探》的袁偉豪就有756票，值得注意的是王浩信在《盲俠》中是一名律師，但仍有362票。另外一組投票是余文樂與陳冠希的宿命對決，結果陳冠希以500票勝出。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191118/large/1574069013_ac92.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191118%2Flarge%2F1574069013_ac92.jpg&h=e63ae68c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191118/large/1574069012_4915.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191118%2Flarge%2F1574069012_4915.jpg&h=2d6ef3ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191118/60281465\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191118%2F60281465&d=O2Kpqs6hAe%2BpM%2F1AUa5ix6of2S8NuZTczTYEA3Eyx%2FE%3D&h=40e0eff7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191118%2F60281465&h=a17ba6b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191118/60281465</a>"},{"pid":"365e3021abd0a700023fb2dd00d94298d493fd42","tid":1734399,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T00:30:10.000Z","msg":"袁偉豪到今時今日仲掛住投埋晒啲咁嘅無聊票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9dd01c11be3cb7d2abd7ffd36dd62d6eda44595","tid":1734399,"uid":246787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T02:03:12.000Z","msg":"點解演律師都係個list到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}